symc.name: SERVICE_AUTO_START
symc.desc: A service started automatically by the service control manager during system startup.

symc.name: SERVICE_BOOT_START
symc.desc: A device driver started by the system loader. This value is valid only for driver services.

symc.name: SERVICE_DEMAND_START
symc.desc: A service started by the service control manager when a process calls the StartService function.

symc.name: SERVICE_DISABLED
symc.desc: A service that cannot be started. Attempts to start the service result in the error code ERROR_SERVICE_DISABLED.

symc.name: SERVICE_SYSTEM_START
symc.desc: A device driver started by the IoInitSystem function. This value is valid only for driver services.
